Umm, can I really?

45
00:05:01,852 --> 00:05:04,039
I heard from my father the other day,

46
00:05:05,633 --> 00:05:06,766
you

47
00:05:08,336 --> 00:05:09,967
don't have any family, right?

48
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:16,578
That's when it finally made sense to me.

49
00:05:17,773 --> 00:05:19,530
My father was planning to

50
