57
00:05:34,835 --> 00:05:36,781
I also renovated my home and

58
00:05:37,023 --> 00:05:38,563
made preparations to welcome him.

59
00:05:40,102 --> 00:05:42,234
But when it came time to move,

60
00:05:42,570 --> 00:05:44,000
he suddenly said he wanted to

61
00:05:44,008 --> 00:05:45,422
continue running the shop.

62
