117
00:08:42,406 --> 00:08:45,148
You really love your work, don't you?

118
00:08:45,609 --> 00:08:47,500
It's not exactly like that.

119
00:08:47,945 --> 00:08:50,328
With Kaneko-san gone

120
00:08:50,477 --> 00:08:52,265
and Sakamoto-kun not coming anymore,

121
00:08:52,281 --> 00:08:54,054
I thought it would be impossible,

122
00:08:54,070 --> 00:08:56,070
but somehow we manage anyway.

123
00:08:57,328 --> 00:08:58,406
Yeah.

124
00:08:59,070 --> 00:08:59,844
But

125
00:09:00,125 --> 00:09:01,187
this time,

126
00:09:01,203 --> 00:09:02,780
it's all thanks to Watari-san.

127
00:09:03,086 --> 00:09:04,203
Definitely.

128
00:09:04,594 --> 00:09:07,734
If Watari-san had disappeared too...

129
00:09:07,891 --> 00:09:10,000
That's not true, really.

130
00:09:10,398 --> 00:09:12,555
Always so modest.

131
00:09:13,554 --> 00:09:16,539
Alright! Shall we go then?

132
00:09:16,664 --> 00:09:18,242
- Yes.
- Let's go.

133
00:09:19,242 --> 00:09:20,430
Sure.

134
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:27,875
Probably,

135
00:09:29,258 --> 00:09:30,781
