142
00:09:59,727 --> 00:10:00,883
That's all...

143
00:10:06,734 --> 00:10:07,828
That's all.

144
00:10:32,734 --> 00:10:33,625
No,

145
00:10:34,977 --> 00:10:36,266
it's not just that.

146
00:10:40,641 --> 00:10:41,953
I'll definitely try

147
00:10:42,734 --> 00:10:44,219
to find Kai.

148
00:10:46,023 --> 00:10:47,391
Every time I wake up...

149
00:10:49,680 --> 00:10:50,594
Good morning.

150
00:10:52,813 --> 00:10:54,148
Every time I eat...

151
00:10:54,625 --> 00:10:55,977
Is it to your liking?

152
00:10:56,226 --> 00:10:56,976
Yeah.

153
00:10:58,289 --> 00:10:59,414
