158
00:11:36,828 --> 00:11:38,219
Take a bath and go to sleep.

159
00:11:38,609 --> 00:11:40,281
I'll bring you a change of clothes.

160
00:11:43,047 --> 00:11:43,852
Kai,

161
00:11:48,719 --> 00:11:49,711
thank you.

162
00:11:52,523 --> 00:11:53,164
Mhmm.

163
00:11:56,102 --> 00:11:58,945
I... To him...

164
00:12:06,318 --> 00:12:07,388
Welcome back.

165
00:12:08,716 --> 00:12:09,693
You're early.

166
00:12:11,560 --> 00:12:14,099
Ah, today, with the release...

167
00:12:17,193 --> 00:12:18,373
Are you going somewhere?

168
00:12:21,005 --> 00:12:22,255
I'm leaving today.

169
00:12:24,021 --> 00:12:24,779
Huh?

170
00:12:26,325 --> 00:12:27,802
But he' getting discharged tomorrow.

171
00:12:28,373 --> 00:12:29,662
Why the rush?

172
00:12:29,990 --> 00:12:31,818
They said I can go back to the shop

173
00:12:31,834 --> 00:12:33,271
until I find a place.

174
00:12:35,310 --> 00:12:36,185
But...

175
00:12:36,630 --> 00:12:38,419
There's no reason for me to be in

176
00:12:38,444 --> 00:12:39,974
Hirokuni's care anymore.

177
00:12:44,294 --> 00:12:45,201
Well then.

178
00:12:50,857 --> 00:12:52,130
Stay here.

179
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:56,654
I want you to stay here.

180
00:12:58,373 --> 00:12:59,763
I've made you wait for a long time

181
00:12:59,779 --> 00:13:01,083
