182
00:13:01,748 --> 00:13:03,826
- but I intend to tell you this today...
- It's impossible.

183
00:13:10,701 --> 00:13:11,771
I knew it.

184
00:13:13,318 --> 00:13:14,802
You've really run out of patience.

185
00:13:18,021 --> 00:13:19,162
That's not it.

186
00:13:25,755 --> 00:13:26,638
I...

187
00:13:28,544 --> 00:13:29,794
six years ago,

188
00:13:31,435 --> 00:13:32,552
I tried to dine and dash

189
00:13:32,568 --> 00:13:33,755
at the old man's shop,

190
00:13:35,685 --> 00:13:38,396
and that's how I ended up working there.

191
00:13:41,490 --> 00:13:42,623
But I think...

192
00:13:44,873 --> 00:13:46,044
If I hadn't gone

193
00:13:47,076 --> 00:13:48,873
to the shop back then,

194
00:13:50,013 --> 00:13:51,911
he would have quit the shop

195
00:13:52,459 --> 00:13:54,076
and lived with his son.

196
00:13:56,013 --> 00:13:56,904
Then,

197
00:13:58,185 --> 00:13:59,731
