198
00:13:59,756 --> 00:14:01,036
about his illness sooner.

199
00:14:02,123 --> 00:14:03,084
No.

200
00:14:04,584 --> 00:14:07,490
Accepting you was his decision,

201
00:14:08,044 --> 00:14:11,419
- and it's not your responsibility...
- But it's still not unrelated.

202
00:14:17,802 --> 00:14:19,458
I'm horrified.

203
00:14:22,669 --> 00:14:24,669
What if the old man didn't recover?

204
00:14:27,459 --> 00:14:28,809
And hadn't regained consciousness

205
00:14:28,825 --> 00:14:29,786
after collapsing.

206
00:14:35,638 --> 00:14:36,584
I

207
00:14:38,052 --> 00:14:39,513
had nothing.

208
00:14:43,037 --> 00:14:44,685
I thought whether I was alive or dead,

209
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:49,912
nothing around me would change.

210
00:14:56,216 --> 00:14:57,677
But being here,

211
00:15:01,599 --> 00:15:02,973
I realize that I can influence

212
00:15:02,989 --> 00:15:04,036
someone else's life.

213
00:15:09,763 --> 00:15:10,748
Hirokuni,

214
00:15:13,826 --> 00:15:15,560
