215
00:15:28,880 --> 00:15:29,974
I shouldn't

216
00:15:31,927 --> 00:15:33,716
have come to see you either.

217
00:15:37,037 --> 00:15:38,310
I'm sorry for being selfish.

218
00:15:44,615 --> 00:15:45,701
Wait.

219
00:15:50,529 --> 00:15:51,966
