222
00:16:22,123 --> 00:16:22,880
Hey.

223
00:16:27,115 --> 00:16:27,834
But...

224
00:16:32,529 --> 00:16:33,521
Are you dead?

225
00:17:02,123 --> 00:17:03,685
Isn't that obvious!

226
00:17:06,084 --> 00:17:07,794
Being involved with people is heavy!

227
00:17:08,209 --> 00:17:09,255
It's scary!

228
00:17:10,005 --> 00:17:10,732
But

229
00:17:11,193 --> 00:17:13,974
