230
00:17:19,841 --> 00:17:22,560
That's why you came to me, right?

231
00:17:25,373 --> 00:17:26,107
But...

232
00:17:26,826 --> 00:17:28,505
- But because of me...
- Yeah,

233
00:17:29,029 --> 00:17:30,232
