236
00:17:37,040 --> 00:17:39,430
(Resignation letter)

237
00:17:39,430 --> 00:17:41,412
(Resignation letter)
If I keep on going like this,

238
00:17:41,410 --> 00:17:43,410
(Resignation letter)
I don't think I can give you an answer.

239
00:17:45,380 --> 00:17:46,997
It's too late to

240
00:17:47,528 --> 00:17:48,778
