243
00:17:56,895 --> 00:17:57,747
How?

244
00:18:00,809 --> 00:18:02,637
Come back to me.

245
00:18:08,801 --> 00:18:09,856
That's...

246
00:18:10,223 --> 00:18:11,270
Oh come on!

247
00:18:11,497 --> 00:18:13,473
Why don't you understand?

248
00:18:14,169 --> 00:18:16,544
No matter what you do to my life,

249
00:18:16,567 --> 00:18:17,567
it's fine!

250
00:18:18,606 --> 00:18:19,919
I told you my life is like

251
00:18:19,942 --> 00:18:21,653
a waste of time anyway!

252
00:18:23,966 --> 00:18:25,286
I'll give you

253
00:18:26,247 --> 00:18:27,614
