268
00:19:55,020 --> 00:19:56,528
It can't be helped.

269
00:19:56,747 --> 00:19:58,231
I don't exercise much.

270
00:20:05,559 --> 00:20:07,309
- Oww.
- Dammit.

271
00:20:22,567 --> 00:20:27,691
