275
00:20:47,111 --> 00:20:48,080
Work?

276
00:20:49,197 --> 00:20:50,080
Is it okay?

277
00:20:53,713 --> 00:20:54,884
Just because you submitted

278
00:20:54,893 --> 00:20:56,001
