279
00:20:56,025 --> 00:20:57,228
doesn't mean you can quit

280
00:20:57,244 --> 00:20:58,330
right away, right?

281
00:21:03,455 --> 00:21:04,377
Nah, it's fine.

282
00:21:06,471 --> 00:21:07,455
Because

283
00:21:08,877 --> 00:21:10,205
today's Sunday.

284
00:21:37,135 --> 00:21:37,986
Oh!

285
00:21:38,119 --> 00:21:38,853
Oh!

286
00:21:38,971 --> 00:21:40,760
