- I'm here with my family.

290
00:21:46,650 --> 00:21:47,658
Alright.

291
00:21:49,166 --> 00:21:50,330
Hey, can you give me a hand...

292
00:21:50,885 --> 00:21:52,502
Oh, Kaneko-san!

293
00:21:55,861 --> 00:21:57,666
But it's quite a coincidence, isn't it?

