00:21:57,774 --> 00:21:59,986
Watari-san is around here somewhere too?

295
00:22:00,283 --> 00:22:03,025
He said he has something to do today.

296
00:22:03,119 --> 00:22:04,103
Is that so?

297
00:22:17,197 --> 00:22:18,111
Alright.

298
00:22:26,057 --> 00:22:27,166
At this point,

299
00:22:27,174 --> 00:22:29,108
I've grown attached to them,

300
00:22:29,275 --> 00:22:31,314
almost like family.

301
00:22:31,541 --> 00:22:32,783
You're exaggerating.

302
00:22:40,322 --> 00:22:41,408
Harsh.

303
00:22:41,830 --> 00:22:43,259
Letting them wither without

304
00:22:43,275 --> 00:22:44,486
eating them is harsher.

305
00:22:46,557 --> 00:22:47,439
For dinner?

306
00:22:48,627 --> 00:22:49,439
Yes.

307
00:22:50,252 --> 00:22:51,111
Looking forward to it.

308
00:23:04,369 --> 00:23:05,361
It's Kaneko-san.

309
00:23:07,666 --> 00:23:08,541
Everyone...

310
00:23:11,892 --> 00:23:13,182
Wait! Hey!

311
00:23:13,432 --> 00:23:14,682
Right now,

312
00:23:14,707 --> 00:23:16,425
we're doing something important.

313
00:23:17,510 --> 00:23:18,908
I'm just going to reply...

314
00:23:19,275 --> 00:23:20,603
It's always Kaneko, Kaneko.

315
00:23:21,432 --> 00:23:23,689
Well, he was my boss, so...

316
00:23:24,353 --> 00:23:25,385
What?

317
00:23:26,322 --> 00:23:28,283
Hirokuni is already mine now.

318
00:23:31,072 --> 00:23:32,213
I know.

319
00:23:32,463 --> 00:23:34,142
I'll reply later.

320
00:23:37,541 --> 00:23:38,478
You're easy to trick.

321
00:23:44,010 --> 00:23:44,642
Wait...

322
00:23:45,244 --> 00:23:46,908
I give up, I give up!

323
00:23:47,420 --> 00:23:48,110
Ah!

324
00:23:49,963 --> 00:23:51,799
Can you calm down first?

325
00:23:52,064 --> 00:23:52,900
Please?

326
00:23:58,984 --> 00:23:59,820
Look.
